Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:06.47,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:08.89,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:18.56,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}若要唤出情感之名 则无休无止无穷无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:26.65,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}你的眼神传来呼唤 我以本能即可分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:28.49,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}相伴相随
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:29.74,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}不离不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:33.33,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}无论光明抑或黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:37.21,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如紧凑相连的拼图零片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:41.46,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:45.71,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}萍水相逢也好 命中注定也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:50.39,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}终将指引我们走向所坚信的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:57.14,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}赤诚真心 逐步升温
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:23:00.98,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}无虚情假意 非利益所趋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:05.73,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}以真实自我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.73,0:23:09.49,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}立于所盼之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:13.16,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}愿君侧耳
